{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, in this way, she was-- she was-- she came to be alive to the last 250 people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she took my sister-- the other sister-- with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, they really decided to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole ghetto's trying to escape.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they thought of all sorts of plans to escape, to amass sort of whoever save themselves, save them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whoever not, at least they'll put up a resistance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister, somehow-- she didn't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Both my sisters had blue eyes and blonde hair-- and they were women-- they put scarves over them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow they got out, by some--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people watched them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They helped them get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they knew that-- that, once they get out, they will find us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they got out, and a few other people after them got out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They watched them go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other people got picked up by the partisans and brought to the Otriad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't get picked up anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the people said they went the wrong way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They must have been picked up by the Germans and killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Since a week passed, and two weeks, and three weeks, and a month, and two months, and they didn't show up, so I assumed they were killed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no other answer to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- in those days, those things we just accepted, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You just mourn it, but you didn't have time to mourn, because you're fighting for your own life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So one day when we came to the Naliboki Pushcha-- when we went to the Naliboki Pushcha, as I described before-- the pushcha was teeming with partisans.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some of our Otriad found some cousins, and someone found some-- some uncles or some-- one found a brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't know he was alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
